  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Telemarketing Executive (Telemarketer)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Telemarketing Executive (Telemarketer) role focused on engaging customers through calls, securing appointments, and supporting the Business Development team to drive business growth.<br /><br /><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><ul><li><p>1-3 years of previous experience in customer service or telemarketing preferred</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently in a fast spaced environment</p></li><li><p>Energetic and high level of work commitment with a positive mindset</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Fluent English command is needed for both speaking and writing</p></li><li><p>Maintain detailed records of outgoing and ingoing calls as well as follow up information and outcomes</p></li><li><p>Meet or exceed projected weekly and monthly calls and appointment goals</p></li><li><p>Accurately document the customer's personal information including phone number, address and other order information</p></li><li><p>Ask relevant leading questions to understand the customer's needs </p></li><li><p>Work closely with Business Development team on appointment secured</p></li><li><p>Follow up email with potential clients on appointment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min “O’ level </p></li><li><p>Goal Driven & positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Able to speak English and Mandarin</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office application including MS outlook and MS Excel </p></li></ul>",
